>128 (R A1@0.6)x4 (R A1@0.7)x4 (R A1@0.8)x3 (R A1@0.9)x3 R:2
>144 (A1 A1@0.55 A1@0.8 A1@0.5 A1 A1@0.55 A1@0.85 G1@0.7 A1 A1@0.55 A1@0.8 A1@0.5 A1 A1@0.6 C2@0.8 B1@0.7 F1 F1@0.55 F1@0.8 F1@0.5 F1 F1@0.55 F1@0.85 E1@0.7 G1 G1@0.55 G1@0.8 G1@0.5 G1 G1@0.6 B1@0.8 E1@0.7)x2
