(R A1@0.7)x4 (R A1@0.55)x4

# ---- the riff: low, bluesy, hypnotic — a 2-bar cell with a D# blue-
# note slide, not a tune. Stated at 48 and 144, climbing through the
# lift at 176, always below C5 except one E5 at the lift's peak.
track lead patch=acidline vel=0.85 len=0.5
# the riff sneaks in two beats early, still under the closed filter
>46 A3:0.75 C4:0.25@0.6 A3:1
>48 (A3:0.75 C4:0.25@0.6 A3:1 R:0.5 E4:0.5 D#4:0.5@0.75 D4:0.5 C4:0.5 A3:0.5@0.7 G3:0.75 A3:1.75 R:0.5 F3:0.75 A3:0.25@0.6 C4:1 R:0.5 C4:0.5 D4:0.5@0.75 E4:0.5 D4:0.5 B3:0.5@0.7 G3:0.75 A3:0.25@0.6 B3:0.5 D4:0.5 F4:0.5@0.75 E4:0.5)x1
