>144 ((CH:0.27@0.55 CH:0.23@0.2 R:0.27 CH:0.23@0.3)x15 CH:0.27@0.55 CH:0.23@0.2 OH:0.27@0.6 CH:0.23@0.35)x3
(CH:0.27@0.55 CH:0.23@0.2 R:0.27 CH:0.23@0.3)x12
>208 (CH:0.27@0.4 CH:0.23@0.15 CH:0.27@0.45 CH:0.23@0.18)x16

track openhat kit=909 len=0.5 vel=0.7
